We'd like to configure the way that search results look like. The search results page is pretty complex for our taste, especially if you want to skim through a lot of results. Offer for example a way to enable/disable the page content preview (so only the page name will be shown). All this should be on a per user basis (so the users can select the search result design the way they want)

