When listing news items, there is no intuitive UI for user to realise that each news item title is a click-able link. There should be a way of demonstrating the fact that to edit the news item, user is required to click the item's title. Perhaps highlighting the titles, or listing them separately may make it more obvious.

Please see related discussion at https://support.atlassian.com/browse/CSP-3207

