Provide a navigation bar that shows the user's navigation history.  We have several users who have used other Wikis previously, and they have found this feature to be invaluable in being able to "retrace" their steps when moving through the Wiki.

Although your "History" pop-up has some of this functionality, it does have some problems.  If you leave the pop-up window open, the history is not dynamically updated as you navigate through the pages: you must click on the "History" button to update the contents of the pop-up.  Also, if you click on a link in the History pop-up, then the pop-up closes, which is frustrating if you're trying to retain the history window as your main form of backward navigation.

The lack of this feature in the product may force us to look elsewhere for our Wiki selection (we are currently in the evaluation stage).

